<div class="los_header">

<p>&nbsp;</p>


<p>*NOTE: Name searches must match our records exactly and are case sensitive.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>


 <p>For example, to retrieve the profile for student "Benjamin Smith" you must search:</p>




<div class="span4">


    <form class="form">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Benjamin" class="input-small">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Last Name" class="input-small">
    </form>

    <p>Or</p>

    <form class="form">
        <input type="text" placeholder="First Name" class="input-small">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Smith" class="input-small">
    </form>

    <p>Or</p>

    <form class="form">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Benjamin" class="input-small">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Smith" class="input-small">
    </form>

</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Be aware that nicknames such as "Ben" or "Benny", and minor misspellings such as "Benjemin" would produce 0 results.</p>
</div>